title: Union Mills Sectional Title Lasts a Lifetime
text: Union Mills Sectional Title Lasts a Lifetime Wendell Trogdon HickoryHusker.com MICHIGAN CITY, Ind. -- As Woodrow W. Jacobs put it, "It was a big moment for me, and a big moment for the community of Union Mills." That big moment has lasted 50 years and remains vivid in the memory of Woody Jacobs who played for the Union Mills Millers when they won the 1950 Michigan City Sectional...
